I"<p>The Omron Adept MobileRobots AmigoBot is a small, durable general purpose
differential-drive mobile robot platform. The AmigoBot can receive motion
commands and provide data via a wifi connection, or by adding your own small
low-power computer.</p>

<p>The AmigoBot can be used in ROS using the “rosaria” or “p2os” drivers,
and model and launch configuration is available. Visit
<a href="http://wiki.ros.org/Robots/AMR_Pioneer_Compatible">http://wiki.ros.org/Robots/AMR_Pioneer_Compatible</a> for more information.</p>

